{"tid":462109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【朱經緯案】庭上講警棍使用方式 朱經緯：「有啲嘢教唔到架」","createTime":"2017-11-08T09:14:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T12:33:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"8ad245fb3bf007868495fd8506a150802599d743","tid":462109,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171108/large/1510131681_91ac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171108%2Flarge%2F1510131681_91ac.jpg&h=0a7dd6d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動期間涉揮動警棍襲途人的退休警司朱經緯，被控襲擊致造成身體傷害罪，被告朱經緯自辯時詳述警棍的使用方式，說自從2014年10月19日後，部分梯隊獲發使用長警棍，而長警棍其中一種使用方法是「check drillls」，是用以應付「表面passive，其實好active既人群」。<br />\n<br />\n朱經緯解釋指，以上所指，即全部人雙手高舉但向警方步步迫近警方的情況，又謂「警棍既用途大家都知係用黎做咩」，但用來打擊則要看每個人的信心、對警棍的知識及能力，並謂「有啲嘢教唔到架」，但他指這不是案發日警棍的主要用途。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171108/57433808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F57433808&d=Rx7qGxE%2BghSue3CEkBmVoaS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=e228b665\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171108%2F57433808&h=62531dc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171108/57433808</a>"},{"pid":"e2c2f49d9f34de53e001cfe402f7b268232947a4","tid":462109,"uid":90601,"like":60,"dislike":2,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:15:35.000Z","msg":"咁撚串 法官點幫你輕判"},{"pid":"0f0f8d339a1cd6f8dab0090d9e659c9e3453e30d","tid":462109,"uid":34336,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:16:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0386df9559dad400493d9464f3283a69b1e99b87","tid":462109,"uid":44358,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T09:16:37.000Z","msg":"完全唔明佢講乜撚